	<h2>About this product</h2>
	<ol>
		<li>G502 LIGHTSPEED is a new and improved version of the original G502 HERO gaming mouse</li>
		<li>Compared to the G502 HERO, G502 LIGHTSPEED is wireless, has an improved battery life, as well as a 7-gram weight reduction</li>
		<li>G502 LIGHTSPEED uses the HERO 16K sensor which is capable of 400+ IPS across the whole 16,000 DPI range</li>
		<li>G502 LIGHTSPEED has the same design as the original G502 HERO but is incorporated with an advanced endoskeleton that results in the 7-gram weight reduction</li>
		<li>G502 LIGHTSPEED also comes with the LIGHTSYC RGB lighting which is fully customizable. Around 16.8M+ colors are available for you to set via Logitech G HUB software</li>
		<li>The Logitech G HUB software can also be used to program the 11 buttons of the G502 LIGHTSPEED</li>
		<li>The weight of the G502 LIGHTSPEED can also be fine-tuned using the 4x2g and 2x4g weights that comes with G502 LIGHTSPEED</li>
	</ol>
</div>
